issue.title: [CF 914] undefined category errors on login
issue.body:
When I login, I get tellmewhen errors:

tellmewhen:  the dr category "shortroot" is not defined!
tellmewhen:  the dr category "knock back" is not defined!
tellmewhen:  the dr category "short disorient" is not defined!

These all happen on lines:

dr.lua:123
dr.lua:97

I'm just not sure where those objects are stored
